  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AWAKEN A VALLEY FROZEN IN TIME.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stasis Valley is a 2D puzzle-platformer that follows Adam, a young man who has recently experienced a great loss. After this event he descends into a surreal valley within his own mind, where he must attempt to make sense of the world around him (as well as his emotions). Uncover the valley's secrets, and confront the dangers lurking within.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460080/extras/24f815c8ae5e52aba53b546ece587e4a.avif?t=1746072135\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100+ levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Space-bending mechanics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A unique, stylized look </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A lovely score composed by Mike Eramo </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A story about loss, avoidance, and acceptance</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460080/extras/314e57ef5d86538e94d8f65ef9e2f153.avif?t=1746072135\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AWAKEN A VALLEY FROZEN IN TIME.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stasis Valley is a 2D puzzle-platformer that follows Adam, a young man who has recently experienced a great loss. After this event he descends into a surreal valley within his own mind, where he must attempt to make sense of the world around him (as well as his emotions). Uncover the valley's secrets, and confront the dangers lurking within.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460080/extras/24f815c8ae5e52aba53b546ece587e4a.avif?t=1746072135\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100+ levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Space-bending mechanics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A unique, stylized look </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A lovely score composed by Mike Eramo </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A story about loss, avoidance, and acceptance</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460080/extras/314e57ef5d86538e94d8f65ef9e2f153.avif?t=1746072135\" width=780 height=118 /></span></p>",
